SMALL IMMORALITIES GROW INTO BIG VICES<br/><br/>DEAR FRIENDS,
<br />HELLO,
<br />HOPE  GOOD HEALTH N HAPPINESS ATTENDS U THERE...
<br />AS SAME ATTENDS US HERE....
<br />PLEASE READ N SEE HOW SMALL IMMORALITIES LEAD TO BIG ONES.
<br />ITS BETTER NOT TO INDULGE IN THEM ATALL...
<br />A LITTLE DOSE OF PLEASURE FOR A SHORT WHILE--
<br />CAN SPOIL THE PLEASURES OF WHOLE LIFE....
